<!DOCTYPE ext_descriptions SYSTEM "../../../dtd/description.dtd">
<ext_descriptions module_directory="generic_product_occurrence" schema_file="arm.xml" describe.selects="YES" describe.subtype_constraints="YES" rcs.date="$Date: 2005/08/31 11:20:13 $" rcs.revision="$Revision: 1.4 $">
<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
  Schema: Generic_product_occurrence_arm
   <express_ref linkend="generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Generic_product_occurrence_arm">
</ext_description>

	<!-- +++++++++++ Definition_based_product_occurrence +++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Definition_based_product_occurrence">
A <b>Definition_based_product_occurrence</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Product_occurrence"/>
that uses another <express_ref linkend="Product_view_definition:arm:Product_view_definition_arm.Product_view_definition"/> of the same <express_ref linkend="Product_version:arm:Product_version_arm.Product_version"/> as its definition.
<b>Definition_based_product_occurrence</b> is an abstract concept which requires further specialization to represent the kind of product for which is an occurrence.
</ext_description>
	
	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Generic_product_occurrence_arm  Entity: Definition_based_product_occurrence  Attribute: derived_from 
   <express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Definition_based_product_occurrence.derived_from"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Definition_based_product_occurrence.derived_from">
the <express_ref linkend="Product_view_definition:arm:Product_view_definition_arm.Product_view_definition"/>
   		 on which the <b>Definition_based_product_occurrence</b> is based.
</ext_description>

<ext_description linkend="Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Definition_based_product_occurrence.wr:WR1">
<p>
<express_ref linkend="product_view_definition:arm:Product_view_definition_arm.Product_view_definition.defined_version"/> inherited from
<express_ref linkend="product_view_definition:arm:Product_view_definition_arm.Product_view_definition"/> shall also be
<express_ref linkend="product_view_definition:arm:Product_view_definition_arm.Product_view_definition.defined_version"/> for <b>derived_from</b>.
</p>
</ext_description>

	<!-- +++++++++++ Product_occurrence +++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Product_occurrence">

A <b>Product_occurrence</b> is the identification of an occurrence of an object in a product structure.
<p>A <b>Product_occurrence</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="product_view_definition:arm:Product_view_definition_arm.Product_view_definition">
   		Product_view_definition
	</express_ref>.</p>
	</ext_description>

	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Generic_product_occurrence  Entity: Product_occurrence  Attribute: occurrence_quantity 
   <express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Product_occurrence.occurrence_quantity"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Product_occurrence.occurrence_quantity">
<p>the <express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.extended_value_with_unit"/> that defines the quantity of the occurrence.</p>
<example number="1">A <express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Product_occurrence"/> of a liquid part may have an "occurrence quantity" equal to 5 litres.</example>
	<p>The value of this attribute need not be specified. 
	In such a case, the quantity shall be considered as unknown, unless the instance is of a subtype of <express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Product_occurrence"/> for which the quantity is derived from the definition.</p>
	<example number="2">The quantity of a <express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Single_instance"/> is one.</example>
	</ext_description>
	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Generic_product_occurrence_arm  Entity: Product_occurrence  Attribute: quantity_criterion 
   <express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Product_occurrence.quantity_criterion"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Product_occurrence.quantity_criterion">
<p>a string that specifies the criterion that constrains the actual quantity of the occurrence. The value of this attribute need not be specified.</p> 
<example>'as required for balance' and 'as required for lubrication' are examples for a "quantity criterion".</example>
	</ext_description>
	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Generic_product_occurrence  Entity: Product_occurrence  Attribute: occurrence_contexts 
   <express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Product_occurrence.occurrence_contexts"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Product_occurrence.occurrence_contexts">
the set of instances of <express_ref linkend="product_view_definition_relationship:arm:Product_view_definition_relationship_arm.View_definition_relationship"/> where the <express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Product_occurrence"/> 
plays the role of "related view". This set shall contain at least an instance.
</ext_description>

	<!-- +++++++++++ Quantified_instance +++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Quantified_instance">
		<p>A <b>Quantified_instance</b> is a type of 
	<express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Product_occurrence_with_quantity"/>
	that identifies a quantified occurrence of a part, the occurrence quantity being defined by a 
	<express_ref linkend="value_with_unit:arm:Value_with_unit_arm.Value_with_unit">Value_with_unit</express_ref>.</p>
	</ext_description>
	
	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Generic_product_occurrence_arm  Entity: Quantified_instance  Attribute: occurrence_quantity 
   <express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Quantified_instance.occurrence_quantity"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Quantified_instance.occurrence_quantity">
	an attribute shall be defined by a <express_ref linkend="value_with_unit:arm:Value_with_unit_arm.Value_with_unit">Value_with_unit</express_ref>.
</ext_description>
	<ext_description linkend="Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Quantified_instance.wr:WR2">
The <b>Quantified_instance</b> shall be either a 
			<express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Definition_based_part_occurrence"/> or a
			<express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Specification_based_part_occurrence"/>.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Quantified_instance.wr:WR1">
The <express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Product_occurrence.quantity_criterion"/> attribute inherited from
<express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Product_occurrence"/> shall not be specified.	
</ext_description>

	<!-- +++++++++++ Single_instance +++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Single_instance">
		<p>A <b>Single_instance</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Product_occurrence"/>
	that identifies a single occurrence of a part.</p>
		<note>The concept of <express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Single_instance"/> is only meaningful for countable parts or materials.</note>
	</ext_description>
	<ext_description linkend="Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Single_instance.wr:WR2">
The <b>Single_instance</b> shall be either a <express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Definition_based_part_occurrence"/> or a <express_ref linkend="part_occurrence:arm:Part_occurrence_arm.Specification_based_part_occurrence"/>.
</ext_description>

	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Generic_product_occurrence_arm  Entity: Product_occurrence_with_quantity 
   <express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Product_occurrence_with_quantity"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Product_occurrence_with_quantity">
	A <b>Product_occurrence_with_quantity</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Product_occurrence"/>.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Product_occurrence_with_quantity.occurrence_quantity">
specifies a role of the <express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.extended_value_with_unit"/> for the <b>Product_occurrence_with_quantity</b>. The value of this attribute need not be specified.
</ext_description>

<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Generic_product_occurrence_arm  Entity: Selected_instance 
   <express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Selected_instance"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Selected_instance">
	<p>A <b>Selected_instance</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Product_occurrence_with_quantity"/>
	that identifies a quantified occurrence of a part, the occurrence quantity being characterized with a <express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Selected_instance.quantity_criterion"/>.</p> 
	</ext_description>
	<ext_description linkend="Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Selected_instance.quantity_criterion">
	specifies the string value. The value of this attribute need not be specified.
	</ext_description>

	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Generic_product_occurrence_arm  Entity: Specification_based_product_occurrence 
   <express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Selected_instance"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Specification_based_product_occurrence">
<p>A <b>Specification_based_product_occurrence</b> is a type of

<express_ref linkend="Generic_product_occurrence:arm:Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Product_occurrence"/> that identifies an occurrence of a <express_ref linkend="specified_product:arm:Specified_product_arm.Specification_based_product_version">Specification_based_product_version

	</express_ref>.</p>
		<note>The occurrence characterization is not derived from a <express_ref linkend="Product_view_definition:arm:Product_view_definition_arm.Product_view_definition">

Product_view_definition

	</express_ref> as for a <express_ref linkend="product_occurrence:arm:Product_occurrence_arm.Definition_based_product_occurrence"/> but from a <express_ref linkend="specified_product:arm:Specified_product_arm.Product_specification"/>.</note> 	
</ext_description>
	
<ext_description linkend="Generic_product_occurrence_arm.Specification_based_product_occurrence.defined_version">

the <express_ref linkend="specified_product:arm:Specified_product_arm.Specification_based_product_version">

Specification_based_product_version

	</express_ref> of which the <b>Specification_based_product_occurrence</b> defines a particular occurrence.

</ext_description> 
</ext_descriptions>
